# ===================== RAILWAY PRODUCTION (MySQL) =============
# Railway auto-injects MYSQL_URL (internal) and MYSQL_PUBLIC_URL.
# The code reads these automatically — no manual DB_* vars needed.
#
# You only need to set JWT_SECRET and CLIENT_URL in Railway Dashboard:
#
#   JWT_SECRET   = <a long random string>
#   CLIENT_URL   = https://your-frontend.vercel.app
#
# Railway handles the rest: MYSQL_URL, MYSQL_PUBLIC_URL, MYSQLHOST, etc.
# ============================================================
